"a'u":{"d":"‘Hmm... I wonder ...’ (interest), {a'u} {cu'i} — ‘Ho-hum’ (disinterest), {a'u} {nai} — ‘Eww! Yuck!’ (repulsion)","k":"{lo} {se} {cinri}","e":"i a'u ro jbopre cu stati prenu — Interesting, all Lojbanists are smart people.%i a'u ma krinu — Hm, what is the reason?%i a'u cu'i do ne ka'ai pa nanla cu se zdani — It's none of my business that you live with a boy.%i a'u nai do co'i speni le fange — You married a stranger, it's none of my business, I'd avoid this topic.%i a'u nai iu nai panci fa le kalci i ai nai mi citka ti — Yuck, that smells like shit! I'm not going to eat this."},
