"bifce":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a bee or wasp of species $x_2 (taxon)$ ","k":"{cinki}, {sfani}, {lakse}","e":"i le bifce cu vofli vi lei xrula — Bees are flying near the flowers.","r":["bifce","bifcy"]},
