"bilga":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is obligated to do ‘x2(property of x1)’ by agreement $x_3 (proposition)$ ","k":"{zifre}, {fuzme}","e":"i mi bilga le ka bevri ti noi cukta vau le ponse ca le cabdei vau le pu se nupre be mi — I must take this book to the owner today fulfilling my earlier promise.","r":["bilga","bilgy"]},
"bilma":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is ill, sick with symptoms ‘x2(property of x1)’ from disease $x_3 (clause)$ ","k":"{kanro}, {mikce}, {spita}, {senci}, {kafke}, {binra}","e":"i ra pu terpa le nu vo'a co'a bilma fi la zukam — She was afraid to catch a cold.%i mi bilma le ka cortu le denci vau le influ'enza — I've got the flu and my teeth hurt.","r":["bilma","bilmy"]},
"binra":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ insures $x_2 (person)$ against threat $x_3 (event)$ with benefit $x_4 (event)$ ","k":"{bandu}, {cirko}, {betri}, {basti}, {bilma}","e":"i le kagni cu binra le sportivo lo'e xrani le ka pleji le jdini — The company insures the sportsman against injuries by paying money as an insurance.","r":["binra","binry"]},
"binxo":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ transforms into $x_2 (entity)$ ...","n":"{binxo} describes that entity turns into another entity, {galfi} is ‘to turn one entity into another one’. {cenba} describes how entity changes its state while remaining the same entity, {stika} is ‘to make entity change its state’.","k":"{cenba}, {galfi}, {stika}, {zasni}","e":"i le tsiju ba zi binxo lo tricu — The seed soon will turn into a tree.","r":["binxo","binxy"]},
"birje":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ some beer brewed from $x_2 (entity)$ ","k":"{pinxe}, {barja}, {jikru}, {vanju}, {xalka}, {fusra}","e":"i ti birje lo'e badna — This is banana beer.","r":["birje","birjy"]},
"birka":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is an arm of body $x_2 (entity)$ ","k":"{jimca}, {janco}, {xance}, {rebla}","e":"i ra pu jai se torni pa birka be mi — She twisted my arm.","r":["birka","birky"]},
"birti":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is convinced that $x_2 (proposition)$ is true","k":"{jetnu}, {jinvi}, {krici}, {djuno}, {senpi}, {sruma}","e":"i mi birti le du'u do ba snada — I am sure you will succeed.%i xu do pu'i jai gau birti fai lei rirni be do le du'u le nu litru na ckape — Have you persuaded your parents that the journey wouldn't be dangerous?","r":["birti","birty"]},
