"bitmu":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a wall separating $x_2 (entity)$ and $x_3 (entity)$ ...","k":"{jbini}, {sepli}, {fendi}, {canko}, {drudi}, {kumfa}, {loldi}, {senta}, {snuji}, {pagre}, {gacri}, {kuspe}, {marbi}, {vorme}","e":"i le bitmu be le purdi bei le foldi cu rotsu — The fence between the garden and the field is thick.%i pa me ti noi bitmu le malsi cu sinxa le pu nu le gugde cu vlipa — One of these walls of the temple is a sign of the past power of the country.","r":["bitmu","bitmy"]},
