"blato":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a cockroach, termite of species $x_2 (taxon)$ ","k":"{cinki}, {civla}, {manti}","e":"i lo'e blato cu mipri le nei ca lo'e donri — Cockroaches hide themselves during daytime.","r":["blato","blaty"]},
