"bunda":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is $x_2 (number)$ weight units in standard ‘x3(property of x1)’ ...","k":"{grake}, {junta}, {tilju}, {rupnu}, {fepni}, {dekpu}, {jmagutci}, {minli}, {merli}, {kramu}","e":"i ti noi tanxe cu bunda li pa no le'e glico — This box is 10 Engish pounds in weight.","r":["bunda","bundy"]},
