"burcu":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a brush for doing $x_2 (event)$ with bristles $x_3 (entity)$ ","k":"{kombitu}, {pinsi}","e":"i ti burcu le nu punji le cinta vau lei cmalu — This is a brush for painting with small bristles.","r":["burcu","burcy"]},
"burna":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is flustered, disconcerted by $x_2 (abstraction, clause)$ ","k":"{cinmo}","e":"i xu do burna le nu do pilno la lojban — Are you disconcerted of using Lojban?","r":["burna","burny"]},
"by":{"d":"‘b’ (letter)","n":"prefixed with {me'o} is a quotation of the letter. When used alone refers to the last noun with the verb starting with this letter like {by} is for the last {lo} {bredi} used."},
"ca":{"d":"‘during ...’, ‘at ...’ (at time), ‘simultaneousely with ...’ (in time), adverb: ‘meanwhile’, ‘now’, ‘currently’ (expresses present tense)","n":"only parts of the two events might concide in time for {ca} to be correctly used.","e":"i lei mi'u rirni pu zvati le barja i ca bo lei mi'u verba cu kansa no da bu'u le zdani — The parents were in the bar; meanwhile the children were alone at home.%i ko smaji ca le nu mi tavla — Be quite while I'm talking.%i ca le nu do cinmo le ka kansa no da zo'u ko morji le se gleki be mi'o mokca — When you feel lonely, remember the happy moments we had together.%i mi pu prami do i mi ca prami do i mi ba prami do — I loved you. I love you. I will love you.%i le pendo be mi be'o joi mi pu mo'u klama pa cizra stuzi ca le nu no lu'a vo'a sanji le du'u le stuzi ka'e jai ckape — My friend and I arrived at a strange place lacking the awareness that it can be dangerous."},
"ca'a":{"d":"‘actually is ...’, ‘actually does ...’","n":"describes demonstrated activity.","k":"{jarco}, {pu'i}, {fau}","e":"i mi ca'a limna — I'm actually swimming.%i la kevin ca ca'a jatna — Kevin is now acting as a captain."},
"ca'e":{"d":"‘I define’","k":"{jetnu}","e":"i ca'e do zutse va — You sit there!%i ca'e do klama ka'ai mi — You go with me!%i ca'e le se gunka cu mulno — The work is hereby done.%i ca'e gusni — Let there be light!"},
"ca'o":{"d":"progress of the event. ‘be doing ...’ (someone or something), ‘being ... ’ (someone or something), ‘already’","n":"describes an event as progressing whether or not it is continuous (for which {ru'i} is to be used); progressive aspect.","e":"i le mi'u verba ca'o citka — The child is eating."},
"ca'u":{"d":"‘to the front of ...’, ‘between me and ...’","e":"i le snime cu mitre li pa ca'u le vorme pe do — There is snow one meter thick in front of your door."},
"cabdei":{"d":"$x_1 (clause)$ is today, the same day as $x_2 (clause)$ ","k":"{djedi}, {prulamdei}, {bavlamdei}, {cedra}, {ditcu}","e":"i le cabdei cu detri li jy dy ze — Today is Sunday."},
"cabna":{"d":"$x_1 (clause)$ is current with $x_2 (clause)$ in time","k":"{zvati}, {balvi}, {purci}, {ca}, {ca'a}","e":"i so'i roi ku lo xamgu fasnu cu cabna lo xlali fasnu — Good events often happen at the same time as bad events.","r":["cabna","cabny"]},
"cabra":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is apparatus for function ‘x2(property of x1)’ controlled by agent $x_3 (entity)$ ","n":"{cabra} is for devices controlled by external force, {minji} is for machines working automatically, {zmiku} is for robots in general.","k":"{tutci}, {minji}, {finti}, {girzu}, {ganzu}, {pilno}","e":"i ti cabra le ka zalvi le gurni vau le xance — This is a hand-controlled machine for grinding grain.","r":["cabra","cabry"]},
