"catni":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ has authority over matter ‘x2(property of x1)’ on the basis of ‘x3(property of x2)’ ","k":"{turni}, {tutra}, {krati}, {jaspu}, {pulji}","e":"i mi co'a catni le ka te cange ti vau le ka te e'ande mi le patfu be mi - — The authority to be a farmer on this land has been given to me by my father.","r":["catni","catny"]},
