"ce'u":{"d":"inside an abstraction of a verb {ce'u} is applied to another place of that verb","n":"definitions of verbs show which place {ce'u} is applied to. If not explicitly stated then {ce'u} is applied to the first place of the verb. To apply to the head of a relative clause use {ke'a}.","e":"la alis la an cu zmadu le ka mi nelci ce'u — I like Alice more than Ann."},
