"cnano":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is normal in ‘x2(property of x1)’ among $x_3 (entity group, full set)$ ...","n":"{cnano} is the generalized opposite to any/all of these concepts: {cizra}, {fadni}, {cafne}, {kampu}.","k":"{tcaci}, {fadni}, {kampu}, {lakne}, {tarti}, {rirci}","e":"i le ki'ogra be li ci cu cnano le ka se junta vau le ca zi jbena — 3 kilograms is a normal weight of newborns.","r":["cnano","cnany"]},
