"cukla":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is round","k":"{djine}, {ranji}, {bolci}, {tarmi}","e":"i le mi'u lunra noi pelxu gi'e cukla gi'e carmi cu zvati le tsani — The Moon, yellow, round and bright, is in the sky.","r":["cukla","cukly"]},
