"cusku":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ says $x_2 (text)$ for audience $x_3 (entity)$ ...","n":"{skicu} is ‘to tell’, {cusku} is ‘to say’, {tavla} is ‘to talk’, {benji} {su'o} {notci} is ‘to notify’. The second place of {skicu} is filled with a topic like {skicu} {su'o} {dansu} (‘tell about dancers’), the second place of {cusku} is filled with a text like {cusku zo dansu} (‘to say ‘dance’’)","k":"{retsku}, {spusku}, {spuda}, {cu'u}, {bacru}, {tavla}, {casnu}, {bangu}, {dapma}, {jufra}, {pinka}","e":"i ba bo mi pu cusku fi le mi'u ninmu fe lu do mutce xendo li'u — And then I said to the woman &quot;You are very kind.&quot;%i do pu cusku le se du'u do ba katna le nanba — You said that you would cut the bread.","r":["cusku","cusky"]},
