"cuxna":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ chooses, decides on $x_2 (entity)$ from complete set $x_3 (entity group, full set)$ ","n":"{pajni} is for judging matters, {jdice} is for actual decisions, {cuxna} is for deciding (choosing) on something out of options.","k":"{jdice}, {pajni}, {nelci}","e":"i mi nu'o mo'u cuxna le ka zukte ma kau — I haven't yet decided what to do.%i nandu fa le ka cuxna — It's hard to choose.%i mi pu cuxna la alis le nixli — I chose Alice from the girls.%i la alis pu cuxna le blanu le taxfu — Alice chose the blue dress out of all.%i mi pensi cuxna le nu mi citka ma kau — I'm thinking about what to eat.","r":["cuxna","cuxny"]},
