"dapma":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ wishes to $x_2 (entity)$ luck or fate $x_3 (event)$ ","n":"can describe any type of fate: good luck or bad luck (‘to condemn’, ‘to curse’).","k":"{mabla}, {dimna}, {cnemu}, {sfasa}, {dunda}, {cusku}, {cirko}, {jdima}, {di'ai}","e":"i mi pu dapma le mi'u fetsi le ka se funca le zabna — I wished her good luck.%i le cizra pu dapma le virnu le nu ri ba zi morsi — The monster cursed the brave person to die soon.","r":["dapma","dapmy"]},
