"falnu":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a sail for gathering wind $x_2 (entity)$ on vehicle or motor $x_3 (entity)$ ","n":"x2 can be wind, water or other forces enabling the sail to work.","k":"{bloti}","e":"i ti noi bloti cu te falnu — This is a sailboat.%i ti noi molki cu te falnu le djacu pa xislu — This mill operates on a water wheel.","r":["falnu","falny"]},
"famti":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is an aunt or uncle of $x_2 (entity)$ by bond ‘x3(property of x1 and x2)’ ","k":"{bruna}, {mamta}, {mensi}, {patfu}, {rirni}, {tamne}","e":"i do famti mi le ka ce'u mensi le mamta be ce'u — You are my aunt since you are a sister of my mother.","r":["famti","famty"]},
"fancu":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a function mapping argument domain $x_2 (entity)$ to function range $x_3 (entity)$ defined by rule $x_4 (text)$ ; x1 is a function of x2","k":"{mekso}, {bridi}","e":"i le nu se la'u li xo kau mi'o snada cu te fancu le nu se la'u li xo kau mi'o troci — Our success depends on how hard we try.%i le jdima be le broda cu te fancu le nu le mi'u broda tai ma kau cu se sabji jo'u le nu le mi'u broda cu se cpedu xo kau da — The price of a good is a function of its supply and demand.%i le nu mi jimpe la'e ti na te fancu tu'a do — I don't depend on you to understand this.%i li fy pe li xy cu fancu li ma'u li ma'u no me'o vei xy su'i pa ve'o pi'i vei xy vu'u pa ve'o — f(x) = (x + 1) (x − 1), where x&gt;1, f(x)&gt;0.","r":["fancu","fancy"]},
"fange":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is alien or unfamiliar to $x_2 (entity)$ in ‘x3(property of x1)’ ","k":"{cizra}, {jbena}, {ckini}","e":"i ra fange mi le ka zukte ma kau — He is alien to me in what he does.","r":["fange","fangy"]},
"fanmo":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is the final, last part leading up to completion of $x_2 (entity)$ ","n":"can refer to place.","k":"{cfari}, {sisti}, {krasi}, {mulno}, {denpa}, {jipno}, {traji}","e":"i do te mukti le ka mo ca le fanmo le ca jeftu — What are you going to do on weekend?%i le fanmo be le mi'u te jivna ba cinri ba'a — I expect the final part of the competition interesting.","r":["fanmo","fanmy"]},
"fanri":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a factory or mill producing $x_2 (entity)$ from $x_3 (entity)$ ","k":"{molki}, {gundi}","e":"i ti fanri le nanba le gurni — This is a mill producing bread from grain.","r":["fanri","fanry"]},
