"fanva":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ translates $x_2 (text)$ to language $x_3 (entity)$ from language $x_4 (entity)$ with result $x_5 (text)$","n":"{traduki} is an alternative to {fanva}.","k":"{cusku}, {bangu}, {traduki}","e":"i mi pu fanva lu coi ui li'u le glico le lojbo zoi gy.yay, hello!.gy. — I translated {coi ui} to English from Lojban as &quot;Yay, hello!&quot;%i xu lu coi do li'u drani xe fanva zoi gy.Hello, you!.gy. — Is {coi do} a correct translation of ‘Hello, you!’?","r":["fanva","fanvy"]},
