"flani":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a flute, fife","k":"{zgike}","e":"i le sance be le mi'u flani cu jai pluka — The flute has a pleasant sound.","r":["flani","flany"]},
"flaume":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a plum of species $x_2 (taxon)$ ","n":"{lo} {flaume} {poi} {grute} is @@plum‘ (fruit), {lo} {flaume} {poi} {tricu} is @@plum tree’. {flaume} alone can denote either of them.","k":"{jbari}, {titla}, {grute}, {tricu}","e":"i le pa spisa be le flaume torta ije uo mi ba'o xagji — A piece of a plum cake, and, voilà, I'm no longer hungry."},
"flecu":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a current in $x_2 (entity)$ flowing towards $x_3 (entity)$ from $x_4 (entity)$ ","n":"{flu'ente} that has a place structure identical to {muvdu}.","e":"i ti flecu le condi pa lalxu pa galtu krasi pe bu'u lei cmana — This is a current in a deep bed running towards a lake from high springheads in the mountains.","r":["flecu","flecy"]},
"fliba":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ fails at doing ‘x2(state of x1, event of x1)’ ","k":"{cfila}, {snada}, {srera}, {troci}, {sisti}, {ranji}, {denpa}, {bebna}, {zunti}","e":"i mi za'u re'u fliba le mi'u cipra — I failed the test again.%i le mi'u se troci pu se fliba — The attempt failed.%i mi fliba le ka zvafa'i le mi'u penbi — I can't find the pen.","r":["fliba","fliby"]},
