"flu'ente":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a fluid flowing to $x_2 (entity)$ from $x_3 (entity)$ via the route $x_4 (entity)$ ","n":"{muvdu} is a more general term. {senta} is for where no directionality is implied.","k":"{rirxe}, {naxle}, {senta}, {rinci}, {xampo}, {letri}, {sakci}, {gapci}, {litki}, {ciblu}","e":"i ti flu'ente pa lalxu pa galtu krasi pe bu'u lei cmana le condi — This is a current in a deep bed running towards a lake from high springheads in the mountains.%i le flu'ente pe le bu'u tcadu cu carmi — The traffic in this city is intense.%i le nazbi be mi cu ve flu'ente — I have a runny nose.%i le mi'u cmana mo'u se flu'ente le glare — The mountain erupted jetting hot matter."},
