"fonmo":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is some foam or froth of material $x_2 (entity)$ with bubbles of material $x_3 (entity)$ ","k":"{zbabu}","e":"i le mi'u glare pu ru'i cupra le fonmo be le djacu bei le gapci — The heat was producing bubbles of gas in the water.","r":["fonmo","fonmy"]},
