"fu":{"d":"prefix for the 5th place of the current clause","e":"i mi ba benji le xatra fu le kibro — I will send the letter via the internet."},
"fu'au":{"d":"‘luckily’, {fu'au} {nai} — ‘unluckily’","k":"{zabna}, {funca}, {ui}, {di'ai}","e":"i fu'au mi se e'ande fi le ka dasni le tordu skaci — Luckily, I'm allowed to wear a short skirt.%i do ca zvati le zdani fu'au dai — You are now at home, lucky you.%i fu'au nai le vi dacti na mutce da'i le ka plixau — Unluckily, this thing wouldn't be of big help.%i fu'au nai no da pu ganse le mi'u nu le mi'u ninmu ba'o kansa mi'a — Unluckily, no one noticed that she was no longer with us."},
"fu'e":{"d":"creates a scope (brackets) of influence for an interjection","e":"i mi viska pa fu'e ia cizra zdani fu'o — I can see what I believe is a strange house.%i mi ca klama le drata tcadu fu'e ta'o de'i li jy dy re te zu'e le ka viska lei rirni be mi fu'o — I am going to another city (on Tuesday, by the way, to visit my parents)."},
"fu'i":{"d":"the state has been achieved easily, {fu'i} {nai} — state has been achieved hard","k":"{frili}","e":"i e'e fu'i mi cpare le mi'u cmana — I can easily climb the mountain, I can go for it!%i ui fu'i nai mi mo'u klama le korbi be le tcadu — Yay, that was hard but now I'm at the edge of the city."},
