"fukpi":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a copy of $x_2 (entity)$ in form $x_3 (entity)$ made by method $x_4 (clause)$ ","k":"{krefu}, {rapli}, {gidva}, {zi'evla}","e":"i mi ralte pa fukpi be ti noi pixra bei pa bukpu pe le jubme bei le nu prina — I have a printed copy of this picture made as a tablecloth.","r":["fukpi","fukpy"]},
"fulta":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ floats in or on gas or fluid $x_2 (entity)$ ","k":"{limna}, {bloti}, {sakli}","e":"i le morsi pezli xu fulta le sefta be le mi'u djacu — Dead leaves float on the surface of the water.","r":["fulta","fulty"]},
