"fusra":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ rots or decays ...","k":"{birje}, {vanju}, {vifne}","e":"i pa perli mo'u fusra — There is one pear and it is rotten.","r":["fusra","fusry"]},
"fuzme":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is responsible for ‘x2(action of x1, state of x1)’ to authority $x_3 (entity)$ ","k":"{bilga}","e":"i la alis pu jai se facki fai le ka na fuzme le mi'u zekri vau le mi'u kamni — Alice was found not responsible for the crime by the committee.","r":["fuzme","fuzmy"]},
