"gadri":{"d":"$x_1 (text)$ is a gadri, a grammatical particle producing noun out of verb $x_2 (text)$ ...","n":"{lo}, {le}, {la}, {lai}, {loi}, {lei}, {lo'e}, {le'e} are the most common gadri.","k":"{valsi}, {cmavo}","e":"i zo le mi'u gadri lu nu dansu li'u — {le} is a gadri.","r":["gadri","gadry"]},
