"kavbu":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ captures $x_2 (entity)$ with trap $x_3 (entity)$ ","n":"{kalte} is ‘to hunt’, {jersi} is ‘to follow, to chase’.","k":"{jersi}, {kalte}, {pinfu}, {sisku}, {se} {rinju}","e":"i mi pu kavbu le ka bilma fi la zukam vau le ka cadzu bu'u le bartu — I caught cold by walking outside.%i le mi'u nanla pu kavbu le mi'u bolci pa xance — The boy caught the ball with one hand.","r":["kavbu","kavby"]},
