"klina":{"d":"the medium $x_1 (entity)$ is transparent, clear, penetratable to signal $x_2 (entity)$ ","n":"{lo} {na} {zunti} is ‘unhindered’.","k":"{kandi}, {zunti}","e":"i le vacri pu klina le darno voksa — The air was clean to pass a distant voice.%i le mi'u nanla pu klina le ka te smuni ma kau — The boy was pretty clear in what he meant.","r":["klina","kliny"]},
