"kufra":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is comfortable with ‘x2(property of x1)’ ","k":"{cinmo}","e":"i mi kufra le ka vreta bu'u le jbini be re kicne — I feel comfortable lying between the two pillows.","r":["kufra","kufry"]},
