"kulnu":{"d":"‘x1(property of x2)’ is culture of $x_2 (entity)$ ","n":"x1 are customs, ideas, arts, skills.","k":"{ka'u}, {natmi}, {cecmu}","e":"i le ka citka le insekto cu kulnu so'e remna — Eating insects is the culture of most of humans.","r":["kulnu","kulny"]},
