"lacri":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ relies, counts on, trusts $x_2 (entity)$ to bring about, ensure, maintain state $x_3 (event, state)$ ","k":"{minde}, {nitcu}, {tinbe}","e":"i mi lacri do le ka ma kau sidju — I rely on you to help me.%i mi xebni le ka lacri le karce pe mi le ka klama le jai se djica be mi fu ma kau — I hate having to rely on my car to get where I want.","r":["lacri","lacry"]},
