"mapti":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is compatible with or matches $x_2 (entity)$ in ‘x3(property of x1)’ ","k":"{satci}, {tugni}, {sarxe}, {drani}, {tarmi}, {ckini}, {mintu}","e":"i le se cusku be do na mapti le se cusku be le jatna pe do le ka se smuni — Your words are inconsistent in meaning with what your boss said.%i ti ckiku le na mapti be ti noi stela — This is a key incompatible with this lock.%i ta mapti le zabna le ka jai se djica mi — That is exactly what I want.","r":["mapti","mapty"]},
"marbi":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a shelter protecting $x_2 (entity)$ against threat ‘x3(property of x2)’ ","k":"{zdani}, {dinju}, {bandu}, {ckape}, {snura}, {drudi}, {sepli}, {bitmu}, {gacri}","e":"i mi pu jai se bapli fai le ka se marbi pa laldo dinju fi le ka cilmo — I had to take shelter in an old building in order not to become wet.","r":["marbi","marby"]},
