"me'ai":{"d":"shows weaker intensity of interjection or interjection modifier","n":"usually specifies an intensity of an interjection weaker than the intensity of the same interjection earlier used.","k":"{dau'i}, {mau'i}, {me'ai}, {cu'i}, {sai}, {ru'e}","e":"i ua do mo'u klama doi la alis i ua me'ai ro drata ti zvati ji'a — Wow, you arrived, Alice! Oh well, the others are here too."},
