"midju":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is in the middle of $x_2 (entity)$ ","n":"{lo} {midju} is ‘center point’, {lo} {centero} is ‘central subset’ (of a set or territory), {lo} {kernelo} is ‘core’.","k":"{lanxe}, {jbini}, {nutli}, {snuji}, {milxe}, {denmi}, {ralju}","e":"i ra pu sanli bu'u le midju be le mi'u dargu — He was standing in the middle of the road.","r":["midju","midjy"]},
"mifra":{"d":"$x_1 (entity, text)$ is an encoded $x_2 (entity, text)$ made using cipher ‘x3(property of x1 and x2, has two places for {ce'u})’ ","k":"{mipri}, {lerfu}, {sinxa}","e":"i zoi .mifr.cni rni dn.mifr. mifra lu coi ro do li'u le ka me'o o bu pe ce'u se basti me'o ny pe ce'u — cni rni dn is an encoded Lojban phrase {coi ro do} where {n} is a replacement for {o}.%i zo coi mifra le nu rinsa vau le bangu — {coi} is a greeting encoded in language.","r":["mifra","mifry"]},
"mikce":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ cures or treats $x_2 (entity)$ for disease $x_3 (clause)$ ; x1 is a doctor ...","n":"the process of treatment can be described using {ta'i} or {tadji}.","k":"{bilma}, {kanro}, {spita}","e":"i le mi'u mikce pu minde mi le ka sipna — The doctor ordered me to sleep.%i le mamta be mi pu mikce mi tu'a le bekpi be mi ta'i le ka punji le jduli — My mother treated my ill back by applying an ointment.","r":["mikce","mikcy"]},
"mikri":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a millionth of ‘x2(same type as x1)’ in ‘x3(property of x1)’ ","n":"by default, x3 specifies the number of units.","k":"{centi}","e":"i le mi'u jurme cu mikri le mitre be li re boi le ka ganra — The microbe is 2 micrometers wide.","r":["mikri","mikry"]},
"milti":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a thousandth of ‘x2(same type as x1)’ in ‘x3(property of x1)’ ","n":"by default, x3 specifies the number of units.","k":"{centi}","e":"i le mi'u jubme cu milti le mitre be li bi no no le ka ganra — The table is 800 millimeters wide.","r":["milti","milty"]},
"milxe":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is mild in ‘x2(property of x1)’ ","k":"{mutce}, {traji}, {kandi}, {ruble}, {midju}, {nutli}, {ralci}","e":"i le mi'u djacu cu milxe le ka glare — The water is warm (not hot).%i mi milxe le ka tatpi — I'm tired to a moderate degree.","r":["milxe","milxy"]},
"minde":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ commands or orders $x_2 (entity)$ to bring about ‘x3(event, state of x2)’ ","k":"{lacri}, {te} {bende}, {jatna}, {ralju}, {jitro}, {turni}, {tinbe}","e":"i le mi'u turni pu minde mi le ka klama ca le drani — The manager ordered me to come on time.","r":["minde","mindy"]},
"minji":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a machine for function ‘x2(property of x1)’ ","n":"{cabra} is for devices controlled by external force, {minji} is for machines working automatically, {zmiku} is for robots in general.","k":"{cabra}, {matra}, {tutci}, {zukte}, {pilno}, {skami}","e":"i ti minji le ka cpacu loi djacu — This is an automated apparatus for getting water.","r":["minji","minjy"]},
"minli":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is $x_2 (number)$ long distance units in standard ‘x3(property of x1)’ ...","n":"describes measurement of an object in one dimension. x3 desribes the scale that might not be metric. {jmagutci} is used in the same way but for subjectively large objects.","k":"{jmagutci}, {clani}, {ganra}, {rotsu}, {condi}, {mitre}, {dekpu}, {merli}, {bunda}, {kramu}","e":"i le mi'u dargu cu minli li re le ka ki'otre — The road is two kilometers long.","r":["minli","minly"]},
"minra":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ reflects or echoes $x_2 (entity)$ to observer $x_3 (entity)$ as $x_4 (entity)$ ","k":"{catlu}, {viska}, {lenjo}, {pensi}","e":"i le djacu pu minra le gusni be fi la sol la alis le marvele barna — Water reflected the sunlight that Alice could see as marvelous spots.%i le mi'u bitmu so'i roi minra le sance — The wall echoes the sound several times.","r":["minra","minry"]},
"mintu":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is identical to $x_2 (entity)$ ; x1 is x2 ...","n":"the same meaning as {du} but only has two places. For equality use {dunli}.","k":"{panra}, {satci}, {mapti}, {simsa}, {drata}, {dunli}, {du}, {simxu}","e":"i tu noi nanmu gi'e dasni le pelxu cu mintu le patfu be do — That man wearing yellow is your father.","r":["mintu","minty"]},
