"mirli":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a deer of species $x_2 (taxon)$ ","k":"{mabru}, {danlu}","e":"i co'a le ka jbena vau le mirli cu kakne le ka sanli — A baby deer can stand as soon as it is born.","r":["mirli","mirly"]},
"misno":{"d":"$x_1 (clause)$ is famous among $x_2 (entity)$ ","k":"se {sinma}, {banli}","e":"i la su'o da cu jai misno le pilno be la lojban — Someone (having such a name) is famous among Lojban speakers.%i le lisri be le nu pa le ralju dinju cu se darxi so'o vlipa dacti pu traji le ka misno le xabju be le bu'u gugde — The story of one of the main buildings being hit by some powerful objects was one of the most famous events for people of this country.%i la kevin co'a jai misno fai le ka finti le cfika — Kevin became famous as an author of fiction.%i la kevin pu zenba le ka jai misno fai le ka finti le cfika — Kevin rose to fame by writing fiction.","r":["misno","misny"]},
"mitre":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is $x_2 (number)$ meters in ‘x3(property of x1)’ ...","k":"{centi}","e":"i ti noi tanxe cu mitre li pa le ka clani — This box is one meter in length.","r":["mitre","mitry"]},
"mitysisku":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ searches for $x_2 (entity)$ among $x_3 (entity)$ ","k":"{cirko}, {kalte}, {kavbu}, {kucli}, {rivbi}, {marvele}, {facki}","e":"i mi mitysisku le sunla skaci le nenri be le vi kumfa — I'm looking for a woolen skirt among things in this room."},
"mixre":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a mixture including ‘x2(group of same type as x1)’ ","k":"{salta}, te {runta}, {stasu}, {jicla}, {sanso}","e":"i le vacri cu mixre so'o gapci — Air is a mixture of several gases.","r":["mixre","mixry"]},
"mlana":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is to the side of $x_2 (entity)$ ...","k":"{lamji}, {cpana}, {galtu}","e":"i le mi'u tanxe cu mlana le mi'u bitmu — The box is to the side of the wall.","r":["mlana","mlany"]},
"mlatu":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a cat of species $x_2 (taxon)$ ","n":"Also applies to feline animals like tigers, lions.","k":"{bramlatu}, {cinfo}, {ratcu}, {gerku}","e":"i le ka kucli cu catra le mlatu — Curiosity killed the cat.%i mi ralte pa mlatu e pa gerku — I keep a cat and a dog.","r":["mlatu","mlaty"]},
"mleca":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is less than $x_2 (entity)$ in ‘x3(property of x1 and x2 with {kau})’ by amount $x_4 (entity)$ ","k":"{se} {me'a}, {me'i}, {su'o}, {jdika}, {zmadu}, {traji}","e":"i pe'i le tcati cu mleca le ckafi le ka kukte vau so'i da — I think tea is much less tasty than coffee.","r":["mleca","mlecy"]},
"mledi":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a mould or fungus of species $x_2 (taxon)$ ...","k":"{clika}","e":"i le mledi pu sinxa le nu le mi'u kumfa cu cilmo — Mold was a sign that the room was damp.","r":["mledi","mledy"]},
