"pai":{"d":"‘number pi’ (approximately ‘3.14159’)","e":"i li pai du li ji'i ci pi pa vo pa mu so — The number π (pi) is approximately 3.14159.%i le nenri be le cirkulo be li re pi'i ry cu klani li pai pi'i ry te'o re — The area of a circle of diameter &quot;2 × r&quot; is equal to π × r<sup>2</sup>."},
"pajni":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ judges matter $x_2 (proposition)$ ","n":"{pajni} is for judging matters, {jdice} is for actual decisions, {cuxna} is for deciding (choosing) on something out of options.","k":"{cuxna}, {jdice}, {vajni}, {cipra}, {zekri}, {manri}, {mansa}","e":"i le mi'u te cange pu pajni le mi'u du'u xu kau le grute cu makcu — The farmer was deciding whether fruits were ripe.","r":["pajni","pajny"]},
