"palne":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a tray or platter with contents $x_2 (entity)$ ...","k":"{tansi}, {patxu}, {palta}, {ckana}","e":"i ti palne le palta jo'u le kabri — This is a tray with plates and cups on it.","r":["palne","palny"]},
