"palta":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a plate or saucer ...","n":"{lo} {kabri} is normally lifted when eaten from it, {lo} {palta} is not.","k":"{ckana}, {palne}, {kabri}, {tansi}, {ckana}","e":"i mi pu jai gau porpi fai le palta — I broke a plate.%i le mi'u palta co'a porpi — The plate got broken.","r":["palta","palty"]},
"pambe":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a pump inserting fluid $x_2 (entity)$ to $x_3 (entity)$ from $x_4 (entity)$ ...","k":"{gapci}, {litki}, {rinci}, {fepri}, {risna}, {rinci}, {tutci}","e":"i ti pambe le vacri le xislu le bartu — This is a pump for filling up the air into wheels from the outside.","r":["pambe","pamby"]},
"panci":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a smell emitted by $x_2 (entity)$ detected by observer $x_3 (entity)$ ","k":"{nazbi}, {sumne}, {cpina}, {vrusi}","e":"i mi sumne le panci be le najnimre i ri se panci le xrula — I can smell a scent of an orange. It has a scent of flowers.%i mi te panci le najnimre le xrula — I can smell an orange smelling of flowers.%i le mi'u kumfa cu je'a se panci le mabla — The room really stinks.%i iu nai panci fa le kalci — Yuck, it smells like shit.","r":["panci","pancy"]},
