"parbi":{"d":"fraction $x_1 (number)$ is a ratio of $x_2 (entity)$ with respect to ‘x3(same type as x2)’ ","k":"{frinu}, {dilcu}, {mekso}","e":"i li re parbi li vo li re — 2 is the ratio of 4 with respect to 2.%i le cmalu cu parbi le temci be le cabna bei le nu cliva vau le temci be le nu cliva bei le nu volta — It's a small fraction of the time from now until leaving with respect to the time from leaving until returning.","r":["parbi","parby"]},
