"saclu":{"d":"$x_1 (text)$ is the decimal equivalent of fraction $x_2 (number)$ in base $x_3 (number)$ ","k":"{namcu}, {frinu}","e":"i me'o re pi mu saclu li mu fe'i re li pa no — 2.5 is the decimal equivalent of the fraction 5/2 in base 10.%i le saclu be li pai bei li pa no cu cimni le ka clani — The decimal expansion of the number π (pi) is infinitely long.","r":["saclu","sacly"]},
