"sakci":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ sucks, inhales $x_2 (entity)$ into $x_3 (entity)$ ","k":"{cokcu}, {lacpu}, {flu'ente}","e":"i le mi'u prenu pu sakci le danmo pe ra'i le mi'u fagri le fepni — He inhaled some smoke from the fire into his lungs.","r":["sakci","sakcy"]},
