"sakta":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is sugar ...","k":"{silna}, {titla}","e":"i mi djica tu'a le tcati be se cau le sakta — I want some tea without sugar.","r":["sakta","sakty"]},
"salci":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ celebrates $x_2 (clause)$ by doing ‘x3(property of x1)’ ","k":"{sinma}, {jbena}","e":"i mi pu salci le nu mi jai nanca li pa no vau le ka litru la nipon — I celebrated my 10th birthday by travelling to Japan.","r":["salci","salcy"]},
