"sanga":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ sings $x_2 (sound, text)$ to $x_3 (entity)$ ","n":"songs can consist of lyrics and melody. x2 describes either a part of it or the whole song.","k":"{pemci}, {rimni}, {rilti}, {siclu}","e":"i mi pu ciska le valsi e le zgike vu'o pe le se sanga — I wrote down words and melody of a song.%i le mi'u nixli ca'o sanga la'e lu mi prami do li'u — The girl is singing the song &quot;I love you&quot;.%i mi pu troci le ka sanga zo ui — I tried to sing {ui}.","r":["sanga","sangy"]},
"sanji":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is aware or conscious of $x_2 (entity)$ ","k":"{menli}, {morji}, {ganse}, {sipna}, {cikna}","e":"i mi sanji le ka pu srera — I am aware that I made a mistake.%i a'o le mi'u nakni cu sanji le se cinmo be mi — I hope he is aware of my feelings.","r":["sanji","sanjy"]},
