"sanmi":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a meal including $x_2 (entity)$ ","n":"the same as {gunma} but applied to food. One can eat both a {lo} {se} {sanmi} (‘part of meal’) or {lo} {sanmi} (‘the whole meal’).","k":"{barja}, {stasu}, {gusta}, {sanso}","e":"i mi pu citka pa sutra sanmi be le sovda jo'u le ckafi — I had a quick meal of eggs and coffee.","r":["sanmi","sanmy"]},
"sanso":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a sauce for use with $x_2 (entity)$ containing $x_3 (entity)$ ","k":"{sanmi}, {mixre}, {stasu}","e":"i mi nelci le sanso be le nudle bei le tamca — I like tomato sauce in noodles.","r":["sanso","sansy"]},
