"sarcu":{"d":"$x_1 (clause)$ is necessary for $x_2 (state, process)$ to take place ...","n":"{nitcu} is ‘to be in need’, {sarcu} is ‘is necessary, is a requirement’","k":"{sau}, {nitcu}","e":"i le ka sipna cu sarcu le ka kanro — To sleep is a requirement of being healthy.","r":["sarcu","sarcy"]},
"sarji":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ supports, holds up $x_2 (entity)$ against $x_3 (entity)$ ...","k":"{bradi}, {darlu}, {fapro}, {sidju}, {tugni}, {bongu}, {ckana}, {cpana}, {loldi}, {sanli}, {selfu}","e":"i ko sarji mi le nu mi badri — Support me against my boredom.","r":["sarji","sarjy"]},
"sarlu":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a spiral or helix ...","k":"{korcu}, {tarmi}","e":"i le calku be ti noi luska cu sarlu — The shell of this mollusk is spiral in form.","r":["sarlu","sarly"]},
"sarxe":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is harmonious or in agreement with $x_2 (entity)$ in ‘x3(property of x1 and x2, contains two places for {ce'u})’ ","k":"{satci}, {panpi}, {mapti}, {tugni}, {ckini}","e":"i le za'u vi prenu cu sarxe le rarna le ka ce'u jikca ce'u — These people are in harmony with nature in interacting with each other.","r":["sarxe","sarxy"]},
"saske":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a lore, mass of facts about $x_2 (proposition)$ based on methodology $x_3 (clause)$ ","k":"{datni}, {fatci}, {djuno}, {cipra}, {pensi}, {jimpe}","e":"i mi tadni le saske be le mi'u du'u mikce — I study the medical science.%i le cmaci cu saske le mi'u du'u le namcu cu simxu le ka ckini vau le nu lanli le mi'u namcu — Mathematic is a science of how numbers are related to each other based on their analysis.","r":["saske","sasky"]},
"satci":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is exact to precision $x_2 (entity)$ in ‘x3(property of x1)’ ","k":"{sarxe}, {dunli}, {merli}, {mapti}, {kancu}, {mintu}","e":"i le mi'u jubme cu satci rau da le ka mitre li re le ka clani — The table is exactly two meters long.%i le mi'u jubme cu satci le mitre be li pi no pa rau da le ka mitre li re le ka clani — The table is two meters long within an error of 0.01 meters.","r":["satci","satcy"]},
"satre":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ strokes $x_2 (entity)$ with $x_3 (entity)$ ","k":"{mosra}, {pencu}","e":"i la kevin pu satre pa mlatu le xance — Kevin stroke a cat with a hand.","r":["satre","satry"]},
"sau":{"d":"‘requiring ...’","e":"i do ba nenri sau le nu do cusku le ckiku valsi — You enter with the requirement of saying a password."},
"savru":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a noise to $x_2 (entity)$ perceived via ‘x3(property of x2)’ ","n":"noise can refer not only to sound but to any &quot;noisy&quot;, i.e. irritating or chaotic objects.","k":"{sance}, {cladu}, {kerlo}, {smaji}, {tirna}, {siclu}","e":"i da savru bu'u le mi'u kumfa — The room is noisy.%i le vi ru'i nai gusni se la'u li du'e savru mi le ka se viska — These flashes are too noisy.","r":["savru","savry"]},
