"se cau":{"d":"‘lacking ...’"},
"se du'u":{"d":"turn clause into quote","n":"x1(text) is the sentence expressing the clause x2 (clause). Used for reported speech.","e":"i mi pu cusku fi la edvard fe le se du'u le karce pe mi cu spofu — I told Eduard that my car is broken."},
"se ja'e":{"d":"‘resulting from ...’","e":"i se ja'e le ka pu cinmo le mabla vau mi pu gunka no da — Because of my bad mood I didn't work."},
"se ji'u":{"d":"‘given that ...’, ‘based on ...’","e":"i ma pemci se ji'u le mi'u se sanga — What is the lyrics of the song?"},
"se ka'a":{"d":"‘going to ...’","n":"in the clause where {seka'a} is used x1 is the one who goes.","e":"i mi pu cadzu se ka'a le mi'u rirxe — I walked to the river."},
"se la'u":{"d":"‘to the degree of ... (number follows)’","n":"shows the degree in which the verb is true.","e":"i le mi'u prenu cu clani se la'u li so'i — The person is very tall.%i le nu cuxna se la'u li du'e nandu — It's too hard to choose.%i ti se la'u li so'o boske — This is jungle, not a real forest.%i le mi'u dinju se la'u li so'i banli — To a large degree the building is great."},
"se mau":{"d":"‘more than ...’","n":"the clause itself describes the comparison.","e":"i nelci do fa mi ne se mau la alis — I like you more than Alice likes you.%i mi nelci do ne se mau la alis — I like you more than Alice."},
"se me'a":{"d":"‘less than ...’","n":"the clause itself describes the comparison.","e":"i nelci do fa mi ne se me'a la alis — I like you less than Alice likes you."},
"se ni'i":{"d":"adverb: ‘logically therefore’","e":"i ro gerku cu danlu i se ni'i nai bo ro danlu cu gerku — All dogs are animals. However, it doesn't follow from that that all animals are dogs.%i mi pu na zvati le mi'u tcadu i se ni'i bo na ku ka'e ku mi penmi la kevin — I wasn't in the city so I couldn't meet Kevin."},
"se pi'o":{"d":"‘with ...’, ‘using ...’","n":"in the clause where {se} {pi'o} is used x1 is user.","e":"i mi citka se pi'o pa forca i mi pe se pi'o pa forca cu citka — I eat with a fork."},
"se rai":{"d":"‘being most in ...’","n":"x1 of the clause corresponds to the most one in comparison specified after {se} {rai}.","e":"i mi ro roi jinga se rai le ka clani — I always win being the tallest one."},
"se va'u":{"d":"‘for ...’, ‘for the benefit of ...’","n":"beneficiary case tag.","e":"i mi se va'u do mo'u klama — I arrived for you."},
"se'a":{"d":"self-sufficiency, {se'a} {nai} — dependency","k":"{lacri}","e":"i fa se'a le mi'u verba pu kelci — The child played by himself.%i fa se'a nai le mi'u cifnu cu cadzu — The infant walks but not by himself."},
"se'i":{"d":"interjection is self-oriented, {se'i} {nai} — interjection is oriented towards others","k":"{drata}","e":"i oi se'i mi pu srera — Oh, I made a mistake.%i oi se'i nai da spofu botpi bu'u le loldi — Someone would be discontented, there is a broken bottle on the floor."},
"se'o":{"d":"‘I know from a dream, vision, or personal revelation’","n":"{za'a} is for expressing external experience, {se'o} is for expressing internal experience.","k":"{senva}","e":"i se'o do ba snada — I have a feeling you will succeed."},
"se'u":{"d":"ends a construct started with: {sei}"},
"sefta":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a surface of object $x_2 (entity)$ ...","k":"{tengu}, {crane}, {flira}, {plita}, {bliku}","e":"i le sefta be le mi'u najnimre cu xutla — The orange has a soft surface.","r":["sefta","sefty"]},
"sei":{"d":"turn verb into interjection","n":"ends in a selbri (main verb).","e":"i sei mi morji do sampla — As I remember, you are a programmer.%i sei mi bebna le mi'u zarci cu se stuzi le drata — Silly me, the store is in another place."},
"seksi":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ in activity or state ‘x2(property of x1)’ exhibits biological or social sexuality ‘x3(property of x1)’ ","k":"{gletu}, {nakpinji}, {plibu}, {vibna}, {vlagi}","e":"i ti noi finpe ca seksi le ka punji le sovda vau le ka fetsi — This fish demonstrates its female sexuality by laying eggs.%i do seksi le ka se asna vau le ka ninmu — You took a sexy feminine pose.%i le mi'u tigni cu seksi le ka dasni pa tordu skaci vau le ka ninmu — The actor shows her female sexuality by wearing a short skirt.","r":["seksi","seksy"]},
"selbrivla":{"d":"$x_1 (text)$ is a morphologically defined predicate word, verb word","n":"{mlatu}, {e'ande}, {zildukse} are selbrivla.","k":"{lujvo}, {gismu}, {zi'evla}, {cmavo}","e":"i zo mlatu selbrivla — {mlatu} is a selbrivla."},
"selci":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a cell, atom, basic subunit of body $x_2 (entity)$ ","n":"{kantu} allows to express properties of particles.","k":"{kantu}, {ratni}, {gradu}","e":"i mu'o nai do ro selci be le xadni cu cmima pa le so'i klesi — Furthermore, each cell in the body belongs to one out of many classes.","r":["selci","selcy"]},
