"sfasa":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ punishes $x_2 (entity)$ for ‘x3(event of x2, state of x2, action of x2, )’ with punishment ‘x4(event of x2, state of x2)’ ","n":"x4 is the state the punished one gets.","k":"{cnemu}, {pleji}, {venfu}, {zekri}, {canja}, {dunda}, {jdima}, {jerna}, {kargu}, {prali}, {dapma}, {cirko}, {jinga}","e":"i le mi'u rirni pu sfasa le mi'u verba le ka jai gau spofu fai le palta vau le ka na e'ande vo'e le ka kelci bu'u le zdani — The parent punished the child for breaking the plate by not allowing playing at home.","r":["sfasa","sfasy"]},
"sfofa":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a sofa","k":"{nilce}","e":"i au mi te vecnu le pa sfofa — I would like to buy a sofa.","r":["sfofa","sfofy"]},
