"sicni":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is a coin ...","k":"{fepni}, {jdini}, {rupnu}","e":"i ti me le sicni poi jdini lei fraso turni — This is a coin issued by French government.%i mi pu cpacu ci le sicni poi rupnu li pa — I got three coins one dollar each in value.","r":["sicni","sicny"]},
