"xruba":{"d":"$x_1 (entity)$ is some buckwheat of species $x_2 (taxon)$ ","k":"{spati}","e":"i bu'u la nipon le prenu cu citka le xruba nudle — In Japan people like eating buckwheat noodles.","r":["xruba","xruby"]},
